(548, 1, '2016-08-30 23:58:48', '2016-08-30 23:58:48', '[vc_row full_width=\"stretch_row\" el_id=\"bg_home-hero\" css=\".vc_custom_1516048583307{background-image: url(http://localhost:8888/belcosta/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/bg_hero.jpg?id=2739) !important;background-position: center !important;background-repeat: no-repeat !important;background-size: cover !important;}\"][vc_column][vc_column_text]\r\n<h5>Who We Are</h5>\r\n<h1>Los Angeles’ <em>Premier</em>\r\nTesting Lab</h1>\r\n[/vc_column_text][vc_btn title=\"Get Testing\" shape=\"square\" color=\"white\" size=\"lg\" i_align=\"right\" i_icon_fontawesome=\"fa fa-chevron-right\" css_animation=\"none\" add_icon=\"true\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_section el_class=\"lead-in\"][vc_row][vc_column][vc_column_text]\r\n<h2>We offer all cannabis testing services required ​for compliance in the State of California</h2>\r\n<p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\">Quality control measures and testing efforts are absolutely essential to be able to produce safe, consistent, and efficacious cannabis products to the public.<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">  </span>Our staff contains nationally renowned experts in the field of cannabis testing who set the standard for accurate testing methods.<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">  </span>All<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">  </span>methods are validated according to guidelines set forth by applicable 3rd party bodies such as<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">  </span>ISO, AOAC, FDA BAM, and AHP.​</span></p>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][/vc_section][vc_section full_width=\"stretch_row\" el_class=\"bg_blue\"][vc_row][vc_column width=\"1/2\"][vc_single_image image=\"2755\" img_size=\"full\"][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/2\" el_class=\"bg_content\"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h2>Cannabis Regulatory Testing</h2>\r\nQuality control measures and testing efforts are absolutely essential to be able to produce safe, consistent, and efficacious cannabis products to the public. Our staff contains nationally renowned experts in the field of cannabis testing who set the standard for accurate testing methods. [/vc_column_text][vc_btn title=\"Learn More\" shape=\"square\" color=\"white\" size=\"lg\" i_align=\"right\" i_icon_fontawesome=\"fa fa-chevron-right\" add_icon=\"true\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][/vc_section][vc_section full_width=\"stretch_row\" el_class=\"bg_white\"][vc_row][vc_column width=\"1/2\" el_class=\"bg_content\"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h2>Process Opimization Team</h2>\r\nThis is a program which fuses the most advanced data-collection and consolidation techniques with Cannabis Research. This allows us to consider patterns and biological indicators within Cannabis that have never been seen. [/vc_column_text][vc_btn title=\"Learn More\" shape=\"square\" color=\"primary\" size=\"lg\" i_align=\"right\" i_icon_fontawesome=\"fa fa-chevron-right\" add_icon=\"true\"][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/2\"][vc_single_image image=\"2755\" img_size=\"full\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][/vc_section][vc_section full_width=\"stretch_row\" el_class=\"bg_light-blue\"][vc_row][vc_column width=\"1/2\"][vc_single_image image=\"2755\" img_size=\"full\"][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/2\" el_class=\"bg_content\"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h2>Consulting</h2>\r\nBelCosta Labs was built with the understanding of over 50 collective years of Cannabis Growing and Scientific Knowledge. We have experienced the plant in every state and offer analytics- backed solutions for virtually any need.​[/vc_column_text][vc_btn title=\"Learn More\" shape=\"square\" color=\"primary\" size=\"lg\" i_align=\"right\" i_icon_fontawesome=\"fa fa-chevron-right\" add_icon=\"true\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][/vc_section][vc_row full_width=\"stretch_row\" disable_element=\"yes\" css=\".vc_custom_1516050674432{margin-top: 75px !important;padding-top: 40px !important;padding-bottom: 75px !important;background-color: #f9f9f9 !important;}\"][vc_column][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner][insomnia_promo