(1749, 1, '2016-09-28 19:53:28', '2016-09-28 19:53:28', '[vc_section full_width=\"stretch_row\" el_class=\"bg_inner-hero\" css=\".vc_custom_1516139500861{background-image: url(http://localhost:8888/belcosta/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/inner-hero.jpg?id=2795) !important;background-position: center !important;background-repeat: no-repeat !important;background-size: cover !important;}\"][vc_row][vc_column][vc_column_text]\r\n<h5>Process Optimization Team</h5>\r\n<h1>Become a game changer</h1>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][/vc_section][vc_section el_class=\"lead-in\"][vc_row][vc_column][vc_column_text]\r\n<h2>​The P.O.T. Project has the potential to change how Cannabis is grown and processed and put you on the forefront of that change.</h2>\r\nThis is a program which fuses the most advanced data-collection and consolidation techniques with Cannabis Research. This allows us to consider patterns and biological indicators within Cannabis that have never been seen.\r\n​\r\nContributing to this project makes you a pioneer in how the Cannabis plant will be grown and processed in the future. The information is collected amongst participants and cross- referenced by a platform that has a previously unheard-of level of security, sophistication, capability and size.​[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][/vc_section][vc_section full_width=\"stretch_row\" el_class=\"bg_blue\"][vc_row][vc_column width=\"1/2\"][vc_single_image image=\"2755\" img_size=\"full\"][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/2\"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h2>P.O.T. Project components (available 2018)</h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Indoor &amp; Outdoor Cultivation</li>\r\n 	<li>Infusion Operations</li>\r\n 	<li>Extraction Labs​</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][/vc_section][vc_section full_width=\"stretch_row\" el_class=\"bg_white\"][vc_row][vc_column width=\"1/2\"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h2>The FAQ: What\'s the catch?</h2>\r\nBenefits of joining the process optimization team\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Priority Testing</li>\r\n 	<li>Auto-Generated Reporting</li>\r\n 	<li>Business Optimization</li>\r\n 	<li>The Research &amp; Development Forefront</li>\r\n 	<li>Consulting Tie-ins</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/2\"][vc_single_image image=\"2755\" img_size=\"full\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][/vc_section][vc_section full_width=\"stretch_row\" el_class=\"bg_light-blue\"][vc_row][vc_column width=\"1/2\"][vc_single_image image=\"2755\" img_size=\"full\"][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/2\"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h2>The FAQ: What\'s the catch?</h2>\r\nThere are two things required from you for participating with the P.O.T. Project:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Minimum Testing Threshold</li>\r\n 	<li>Additional Survey Info</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n[/vc_column_text][vc_btn title=\"Learn More\" shape=\"square\" color=\"white\" size=\"lg\" link=\"url:http%3A%2F%2Flocalhost%3A8888%2Fbelcosta%2Fwordpress%2Fp-o-t-program%2F|||\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][/vc_section][vc_row full_width=\"stretch_row\" disable_element=\"yes\" css=\".vc_custom_1516050674432{margin-top: 75px !important;padding-top: 40px !important;padding-bottom: 75px !important;background-color: #f9f9f9 !important;}\"][vc_column][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner][insomnia_promo insomnia_promo_text=\"Latest From Blog\" insomnia_promo_paragraph=\"\"][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][vc_row_inner css=\".vc_custom_1472026453604{margin-top: 30px !important;}\"][vc_column_inner width=\"1/3\"][vc_latest_news id=\"1378\"][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/3\"][vc_latest_news id=\"1381\"][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/3\"][vc_latest_news id=\"1383\"][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'P.O.T Program', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'p-o-t-program', '', '', '2018-01-24 23:51:41', '2018-01-24 23:51:41', '', 0, 'http://wordpress.dankov-theme.com/insomnia/?page_id=1749', 0, 'page', '', 0),
