(2777, 1, '2018-01-16 00:28:47', '2018-01-16 00:28:47', '<p>[vc_section full_width=\"stretch_row\" el_class=\"bg_inner-hero\" css=\".vc_custom_1516139500861{background-image: url(http://localhost:8888/belcosta/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/inner-hero.jpg?id=2795) !important;background-position: center !important;background-repeat: no-repeat !important;background-size: cover !important;}\"][vc_row][vc_column][vc_column_text]</p>\r\n<h5>About Us</h5>\r\n<h1>Get to know us</h1>\r\n<p>[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][/vc_section][vc_section el_class=\"lead-in\"][vc_row][vc_column][vc_column_text]</p>\r\n<h2>BelCosta Labs Will be the Premier Testing Lab in L.A. County</h2>\r\n<p>​Combining the required analytic methods with a high level understanding of the Cannabis Industry we are looking to build a synergy that has yet to be seen by any mainstream Cannabis Testing Laboratory.<br />\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][/vc_section][vc_section full_width=\"stretch_row\" el_class=\"bg_blue\"][vc_row][vc_column width=\"1/2\"][vc_single_image image=\"2755\" img_size=\"full\"][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/2\" el_class=\"bg_content\"][vc_column_text]</p>\r\n<h2>OUR METHODS ARE TIRELESSLY VALIDATED TO ASSURE THE HIGHEST ACCURACY IN OUR RESULTS</h2>\r\n<p>Our State of-the-Art high-capacity facility and committed staff will allow BelCosta Labs to deliver precise and validated results in the shortest amount of time possible. We’re built to satisfy difficult, time sensitive Deadlines and QA Practices. Our Clients will receive the results of their submitted samples through the most streamlined and advanced digital data base in the Cannabis Industry, allowing them intuitively-designed access and organization of their information.[/vc_column_text][vc_btn title=\"Learn More\" shape=\"square\" color=\"white\" size=\"lg\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][/vc_section][vc_section full_width=\"stretch_row\" el_class=\"bg_white\"][vc_row][vc_column width=\"1/2\" el_class=\"bg_cont