r accurate testing methods. [/vc_column_text][vc_btn title=\"Learn More\" shape=\"square\" color=\"white\" size=\"lg\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][/vc_section][vc_section full_width=\"stretch_row\" el_class=\"bg_white\"][vc_row][vc_column width=\"1/2\"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h2>Cannabis Regulatory Testing</h2>\r\nQuality control measures and testing efforts are absolutely essential to be able to produce safe, consistent, and efficacious cannabis products to the public. Our staff contains nationally renowned experts in the field of cannabis testing who set the standard for accurate testing methods. [/vc_column_text][vc_btn title=\"Learn More\" shape=\"square\" color=\"white\" size=\"lg\"][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/2\"][vc_single_image image=\"2755\" img_size=\"full\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][/vc_section][vc_section full_width=\"stretch_row\" el_class=\"bg_light-blue\"][vc_row][vc_column width=\"1/2\"][vc_single_image image=\"2755\" img_size=\"full\"][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/2\"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h2>Cannabis Regulatory Testing</h2>\r\nQuality control measures and testing efforts are absolutely essential to be able to produce safe, consistent, and efficacious cannabis products to the public. Our staff contains nationally renowned experts in the field of cannabis testing who set the standard for accurate testing methods. [/vc_column_text][vc_btn title=\"Learn More\" shape=\"square\" color=\"white\" size=\"lg\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][/vc_section][vc_row full_width=\"stretch_row\" disable_element=\"yes\" css=\".vc_custom_1516050674432{margin-top: 75px !important;padding-top: 40px !important;padding-bottom: 75px !important;background-color: #f9f9f9 !important;}\"][vc_column][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner][insomnia_promo insomnia_promo_text=\"Latest From Blog\" insomnia_promo_paragraph=\"\"][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][vc_row_inner css=\".vc_custom_1472026453604{margin-top: 30px !important;}\"][vc_column_inner width=\"1/3\"][vc_latest_news id=\"1378\"][/vc_column_