mage=\"2813\" img_size=\"full\" alignment=\"center\"][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_tta_section][vc_tta_section title=\"Water Testing\" tab_id=\"ac2\"][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/2\"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h2>The importance of clean water for your plants can never be understated.</h2>\r\nAt BelCosta Labs, we can analyze your water medium to ensure purity and detect the presence of both essential nutrients and damaging contaminants. Our analysis uses a combination of ICP-MS testing and benchtop chemical methods.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/2\"][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][vc_row_inner el_class=\".bg_callout\"][vc_column_inner width=\"1/2\"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h3>Our water testing analysis includes:</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>pH and Salinity</li>\r\n 	<li>Bicarbonate content (HCO3)</li>\r\n 	<li>Essential Nutrients: NO3, NH4, B, Ca, Cl, Cu, Fe, Mg, Mn, Mb, S, Zn, Ni, N, PO4</li>\r\n 	<li>Heavy Metal contaminants: Pb, Hg, As, Cd</li>\r\n 	<li>Pathogenic bacteria: E. Coli, Eb</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/2\"][vc_single_image image=\"2813\" img_size=\"full\" alignment=\"center\"][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_tta_section][/vc_tta_accordion][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'Agricultural Media Testing', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '2821-revision-v1', '', '', '2018-01-23 01:15:02', '2018-01-23 01:15:02', '', 2821, 'http://localhost:8888/belcosta/wordpress/2018/01/23/2821-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
