(2881, 1, '2018-01-24 17:37:40', '2018-01-24 17:37:40', '<p>[vc_section full_width=\"stretch_row\" el_class=\"bg_inner-hero\" css=\".vc_custom_1516139500861{background-image: url(http://localhost:8888/belcosta/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/inner-hero.jpg?id=2795) !important;background-position: center !important;background-repeat: no-repeat !important;background-size: cover !important;}\"][vc_row][vc_column][vc_column_text]</p>\r\n<h5>SERVICES</h5>\r\n<h1>Agricultural Testing</h1>\r\n<p>[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][/vc_section][vc_section disable_element=\"yes\" el_class=\"lead-in\"][vc_row][vc_column][vc_column_text]</p>\r\n<h2>What We Can Do</h2>\r\n<p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\">Here’s a list of services that we provide for our clients.</span></p>\r\n<p>[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][/vc_section][vc_row full_width=\"stretch_row_content\" el_id=\"service-accordion\"][vc_column][vc_tta_accordion c_icon=\"chevron\" active_section=\"1\"][vc_tta_section title=\"Soil Testing\" tab_id=\"ac1\"][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/2\"][vc_column_text]</p>\r\n<h2>The quality of plant soil is an essential component to optimum growth.</h2>\r\n<p>At BelCosta Labs, we are offering growers the ability to better understand their soil media by analyzing the essential components for good soil. Our analysis uses a combination of ICP-MS testing and benchtop chemical methods.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/2\"][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][vc_row_inner el_class=\".bg_callout\"][vc_column_inner width=\"1/2\"][vc_column_text]</p>\r\n<h3>Our soil testing includes:</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Salinity, pH, and moisture content</li>\r\n<li>Mineral Salts: Ca, Mg, Cl, Na, SO4, PO4, B, NO3</li>\r\n<li>Essential Nutrients: Bo, Ca, Cl, Cu, Fe, Mg, Mn, Mb, N, Ni, P, K, S, Zn, Na</li>\r\n<li>Heavy Metal contaminants: Pb, Hg, As, Cd</li>\r\n<li>Soil micro-organism cultures</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/2\"][vc_single_image image=\"2813\" img_size=\"full\" alignment=\"center\"][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_tta_section][vc_tta_section title=\"Water Testing\" tab_id=\"ac2\"][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/2\"][vc_column_text]</p>\r\n<h2>The importance of clean water for your plants can never be understated.</h2>\r\n<p>At BelCosta Labs, we can analyze your water medium to ensure purity and detect the presence of both essential nutrients and damaging contaminants. Our analysis uses a combination of ICP-MS testing and benchtop chemical methods.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/2\"][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][vc_row_inner el_class=\".bg_callout\"][vc_column_inner width=\"1/2\"][vc_column_text]</p>\r\n<h3>Our water testing analysis includes:</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>pH and Salinity</li>\r\n<li>Bicarbonate content (HCO3)</li>\r\n<li>Essential Nutrients: NO3, NH4, B, Ca, Cl, Cu, Fe, Mg, Mn, Mb, S, Zn, Ni, N, PO4</li>\r\n<li>Heavy Metal contaminants: Pb, Hg, As, Cd</li>\r\n<li>Pathogenic bacteria: E. Coli, Eb</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/2\"][vc_single_image image=\"2813\" img_size=\"full\" alignment=\"center\"][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_tta_section][/vc_tta_accordion][/vc_column][/vc_row]</p>\r\n', 'Agricultural Media Testing', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '2821-revision-v1', '', '', '2018-01-24 17:37:40', '2018-01-24 17:37:40', '', 2821, 'http://localhost:8888/belcosta/wordpress/2018/01/24/2821-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
